{"tid":2337565,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國貧困縣全部「摘帽」如期完成脫貧 VS 香港貧窮人口達149萬人，創11年新高","createTime":"2020-12-23T11:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T16:17:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d0f51da43c595b0c0e7af5ab17196a968b890e63","tid":2337565,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:13:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=417686\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417686&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpxn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=3a4ab0b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417686&h=55aff292\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=417686</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】扶貧委員會開會討論2019年香港的貧窮狀況，消息指，去年的貧窮人口達149萬，創11年來的新高。<br />\n<br />\n本港的貧窮人口再創新高，去年達149.1萬，比前年增加了約9萬人，貧窮率是21.4%，即不足五個香港人中便有一人貧窮。<br />\n<br />\n數字是自2009年以來最高，如果計及綜緩、生果金及長者生活津貼等恆常現金政策介入後，貧窮人口為109.8萬，亦是11年來的新高。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">習近平：中國如期完成脫貧攻堅目標 消除了絕對貧困</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/557299/習近平-中國如期完成脫貧攻堅目標-消除了絕對貧困\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%2F557299%2F%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A6%82%E6%9C%9F%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E8%84%AB%E8%B2%A7%E6%94%BB%E5%A0%85%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99-%E6%B6%88%E9%99%A4%E4%BA%86%E7%B5%95%E5%B0%8D%E8%B2%A7%E5%9B%B0&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVpxn9kyGvuUmJUtyTBy059fc%3D&h=fe8a91bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/557299/習近平-中國如期完成脫貧攻堅目標-消除了絕對貧困</a>"},{"pid":"6970d3579fd2a40ac42a3fc0f62689872f76d183","tid":2337565,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T11:17:59.000Z","msg":"香港 = 貧困市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1faba9b373d9c40542d5be9e74652f7d791e124"